{"h2eb9285agf219g4d44g9582g45d6d9ea50d2": ["Aha! Right as - what were we saying?", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "f92a0a3c-55d0-2602-417b-cd0c6816a295"], "ha33d12eag1e31g49d8g8f86ge6fa26e8a734": ["What are you doing down here?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "e5070da3-b2bc-09d7-0467-2878d59d6c54"], "h66bd9975gc118g4830g8441g405111980006": ["I was just looking for - Derryth! She's - she'll be worried sick!", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "2346b636-dc78-9e69-6f52-1aa6577d0533"], "h9b981b4ag7ca0g40bdgaf34g8a575f81c4b5": ["I must - need to <i>go.</i>", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "e5d71438-5c49-eb2a-9a2f-5f3cd7e498c1"], "h394887dagff00g4a77g9015gd1ddcee6ee1d": ["For you - your trouble!", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "7063539c-66e2-b669-473c-5e4a46f0bdb7"], "h2bfbcf6cg1047g46f8gbaf2g6fe545037eaa": ["Ta!", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "0f1ab0e2-144d-2bbb-267b-5864c8819f0b"], "hf1c603ccgc304g4ea7g8cc2gc888b468b032": ["I went to quite some effort, helping you. The way I see it, you owe me.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "d06202df-db43-b986-6cf7-70e637b93f24"], "h09cfe109gd9bfg4529g952egc41aacf1a710": ["Yes - of course.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "f3ea9e7f-1e1d-26a1-f9a1-6e609a731365"], "h0ab16853g3dccg4d57g8ad0gebbb863aa9e6": ["Hit your head or something? You seem more than a little confused.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "454754ec-c14d-f11e-6997-5ce732ea89c0"], "h26a125bcg5544g4