, "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "63c38047-e37f-b4b8-4135-b760a3bdeac1"], "h54dec92egb717g4995gb898g0f537578d528": ["I. Know. That.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "21f7fb2b-5567-ecc0-564c-3644dc308d40"], "h1381da1cg45bdg4c1fg8a7egc036a95770cb": ["Surely you can navigate around some fungi, can't you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "7d3ae866-2af7-044b-ed06-1f2b7887e456"], "hac8e0274ga2c8g4ba8gbfa0gd88dd809aa8e": ["Please! Your help!", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "a39a4c1e-6971-8cce-79c2-0675daf18a5d"], "h26e8274bg9d4eg4ca4g9a7bgb39e349f3b2c": ["<i>Turn away.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "e9fb31c3-8194-8fa2-2dd9-87afa2a0d46d"], "hd3dc3bf6gc540g4ec7g814ag05dd6d452eea": ["Wait! Please, hear me out!", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "0d9de6e8-755e-d217-b50a-9a1fa00eeecc"], "hbbc14116ge57cg46b9g97bfg7b2ac15b1b88": ["Bibber-<i>what? </i>Speak plainly, won't you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "7425002a-72b0-79fe-ce73-d97958e146c8"], "h2e129074gdea7g4557g9573gd64195596dc1": ["These mushrooms - toxic!", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "c6e88d40-9adc-721b-3e04-cde2793ada1d"], "h005f8eb3ga0f2g4667g9892g06faa2ba48d3": ["Scroll - escape! My bag! Please. I've dropped it - somewhere!", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "22a8a447-30f5-3a69-d232-52da012ad681"], "hf3604d4ag4145g4732g8ec0gbca90324f9f7": ["I don't suppose you're Baelen, are you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "d8b47096-fae7-0eb0-be65-c2a02ada5f4b"], "h2e82961dg427cg4386g98bdgddb61e6f4347": ["Aye. Bonecloak.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "3ac48eea-bfde-f1b4-96fc-23aea07eaf3f"], "he658bc40g09aeg4371g81dcg6366a98e5629": ["I met your wife. ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "58e3f44d-ecaf-944e-c6de-4cf514db4258"], "h8a633204gaa77g416cgaf16g59ca5dcddaed": ["Derryth! Must be worried rotten.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "58896f8d-79d4-c802-706b-29a61d950894"], "hccfa8c92gfb50g4fe0g9502g4eb63065c307": ["My bag. Please!", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "92d10751-d214-1bda-bf1c-4c471b470ee0"], "hd8b7cee8ga2ebg4b16g99c5gcf2a63f762d1": ["Farewell.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "97628475-7690-73a4-e1d3-bf345854bed5"], "ha7c4cccag9f3ag449bgb699g6f49b7b6a994": ["Wait! I - need... Derryth! My bag! I beg you!", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "9a473695-80fc-6854-d57e-b6d2130c9da5"], "h8dd16ba9g258fg4957gaa93g4bd9841ff82f": ["Hold tight. I'll find your bag.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "f41034e3-3828-2695-5eef-82f1b5b225ba"], "h4b816193g1088g45d9g9934g10068dea0b44": ["Thank you. Thank you!", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "ad414786-7ddb-afb1-91a2-d30e8112f3ac"], "h7c6a552dgb5c2g42c6g9b85ga79ad9978895": ["<i>Hold up a scroll of Misty Step.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "dafac7c3-d009-a5b1-313b-be713ed50783"], "h4a86fc7bg026ag4debg94d8g1cb63d65cda6": ["Yes! That's - yes!", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "8a403cab-b0d5-4205-1f42-bf48e6e118f3"], "hfcdb789dgd6edg416dg848dga27818211355": ["<i>Give the scroll to him.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "75457f6b-8e78-1427-639f-0b383a85a139"], "hb4850405g1838g4789g92deg42b880a81825": ["Just have to... and then... here!", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "74c64fa2-6b0d-1f0d-243b-119674228c17"], "h6a93cc66g1270g4edegadf3gfabdd179d37e": ["<i>Throw the scroll to him.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "b57d0811-2649-4c8b-bb3e-ab28104d7b3d"], "hfe81a865g4c45g4aadg9614g89a27f7ae113": ["AH! Oh, I'm fine.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "fda58f27-be56-9cc6-730d-442a88447851"], "h791dcd5dg28d1g4463gbca5g2c65c4255e66": ["*The scroll misses the dwarf by a fair margin and lands in a clearing amongst the bibberbang.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "36681a85-eca7-c316-8b8d-6573d20383bf"], "he155712fg2c84g4017g945ag2a8e93a68ff5": ["Please - can't... can't get out...", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "6cc3da63-e05e-ebe1-d64b-4e03b2dbb7cf"], "h259f2989g56b9g4eb3g9517gf823e9668cf1": ["I've changed my mind. I'll fetch your bag instead.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "e4174dbd-0db8-6d95-ecab-29c2ad2ff60a"], "h0a347ffcgce00g41cega846g8e060c09b928": ["Scrolls don't come cheap, you know. ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "88c719bf-193a-085b-a804-817bccf60d6a"], "haae80c38gb64bg456cga40agfd7e5c4eb532": ["I'll give you what I have if you get me out of here - please!", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "f83749cc-4518-f2bd-4179-48fdba609306"], "h0b4df491g2715g44d2g9216g97964a7f1feb": ["<i>Keep the scroll for yourself.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "f9c366c2-bf5a-fbda-a7f5-a31deebb1a0a"], "h52cf9342ga63cg492bg8e68g6309b2e22e6b": ["This is your mess - figure it out yourself.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "81a5460d-5a19-bb49-0f55-72bf36215cbe"], "hf498c135gb226g4b50gbad7g80dcdeecdff5": ["Bloody greyskin!", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "a56666e3-3ec4-7329-75f2-c13b35aa4cc7"], "ha4943df8ge121g4739gb480g104b15b921af": ["I-I mean... I didn't mean that.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "1e309911-04cc-f044-34c4-c7eb1264433b"], "ha50b92efg7e4dg40d5g86b4gb87cbf569e77": ["Bloody drow!", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "b755b614-81bf-f5a2-db08-d049f3f4db42"], "h10169f1agbe16g4922ga166gce66ba9e151b": ["<i>Step closer.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "b779b542-b926-41a9-28bf-aff81b507c63"], "h49efda16g0ff9g442cgaafcg780b996c3bf1": ["Stop - please! Don't move, just listen!", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "cb0045e0-0066-fecc-43fb-5b8ea6c8f5da"], "hf9c5b2edg3a2ag4d6dg9246g4ee94a35973d": ["<i>Turn away.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "5f64c612-a07a-f0bd-03d8-56ca27060024"], "h1eada052g2187g4a30g9a4fg1315b8b6a1cb": ["WAIT! Please - please!", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "f90f9edb-8e6d-5efc-3114-67e41816d180"], "h57c3f17cgdf15g4c23ga2cfg06d95b38b967": ["<i>Bibberbang</i>!", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "1fbbdc02-cf65-0c73-7162-d288213e4782"], "h3f6eaadcg03c0g449bg8777g6d94025cc890": ["*He's indeed surrounded by bibberbang - the spores of those mushrooms are both toxic and flammable.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "d4534df3-bc3a-ec92-2d4a-c0d41cc257e7"], "h66de2fd4gc52fg407bg9a5egd48c70832a3b": ["My pack! Please!", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "12b1692d-6d8a-b462-81a5-528a664aeff7"], "h732b3ceag7089g463egb430g012148444f72": ["Gettin' outta here soon enough. Wouldn't have came here if I'd had my wits to work.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "a82acd32-b4a3-62ea-c11c-c532582fcc51"], "hf6b26e35gd0e4g4010g9013gf2cf38a51413": ["Thanks for your help. Stop by Bonecloak's if you're ever in Baldur's Gate.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "6d4c51fd-9d71-e97b-98e2-90bdfaa17a4b"], "h2413de92g3278g4f8aga62ag95618ca128e9": ["I owe you for saving me from my old cow.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "fa92ea48-68eb-754f-6408-41d380b91f26"], "h39e0048dg4566g45dcg937fg85fb39d485f8": ["Derryth...", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "0656d5af-080d-0508-8189-75b3d2fe8e60"], "hb3343166gcd3cg408dg86f7g7f7e794e19d6": ["What... happened?", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "38f0ae60-9489-238e-d743-54f30272c8c3"], "h5447cee7g1c7bg456bgb621g73b15262a427": ["I don't know. I'm sorry.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "e1e233d7-c114-81c2-72c1-5b67836c59d1"], "h465a2750g9813g4ad4g9423g01dc1ecb0811": ["She and I had... <i>an altercation.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "9aea4254-c77d-f509-a8fb-46248061fd17"], "h9ec593a1g7f9ag4889g85ddg0170adfe6ee4": ["Y-you what? <i>You </i>did this?", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "48611144-1389-bb96-a181-3301ba40dc96"], "h069fbabag8737g4316g962bg6c6c1d20d938": ["Derryth... <i>no.</i>", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "88816655-6b11-045a-851c-ebdd647ac629"], "h4b490b78g4ff5g4f75g9c8fgcb873e3e6ebb": ["<i>Give him the Noblestalk.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "c307898c-908e-d906-2e26-a9bb1a9eda5a"], "he93431bagad0bg44fcg9a29gb93e7170ee62": ["No. Don't - can't... Derryth.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "50eb8e19-bae8-5875-404a-b4811b921810"], "hbeb2f2a5gaf4cg48a9g8167g964f8ec5e868": ["<i>No...</i>", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "06bd0a3b-124f-129f-8864-4164cbb2f7f7"], "hddafd314g4d73g4591g849eg83ff5a6da96b": ["I killed her. And I enjoyed every moment of it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "ef697b37-1d79-51c4-5e44-b0379936da03"], "ha22cfb06g7d47g4084ga5fdga4170dd58a42": ["You... what? You <i>WHAT?!</i>", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "30328954-4f04-075e-d5c9-05ac6b771dac"], "h0e46c6c6g0aa4g4dcfgb2cdg515b5c333b30": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "ad94e628-4d29-42c5-0e74-1fec1295b4cf"], "h8457d915gc199g472bg8f96ged839d7328ea": ["She should've come with me. I shouldn't have left her.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "ab0dcd9a-4909-450e-c0f2-0214d0cf03d7"], "h90ce196fg03d9g47a3g8f25gf9ff4404bab7": ["My friend!", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "39461edf-1f2b-14ca-9925-e2b8de63bc5e"], "ha6d7456dgd1dbg4841ga053g2818b1a4f351": ["Bibberbang - curious. Beautiful - but dangerous.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "47258c83-4e84-da28-7e67-d17fb19cd7b7"], "hcb0837e4ga9b7g48b0ga8bdgff09338a09fa": ["Next time - more careful next time. For certain. Thank you - for your help.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "7f832002-0469-7467-4293-4ac360c8aa8b"], "he7396968g747bg4219gb103ged7cbf493031": ["I'm glad I found you when I did.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "a768ce38-d779-54fb-71ae-3fdc2f022df5"], "h484467dfgd535g495ag9af3g02aa25a2b8e8": ["Me too. Yes - very glad.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "5ed8a026-7a72-d205-a2e8-32f08cd011fd"], "h133259d1g7bd0g4249ga634g12deb620c82f": ["Someone's got to look after Derryth.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "98936b3a-aeaa-50cb-1b3a-4253a796beb7"], "hcccaabe9g565dg4cc6gb85dge3d2f5375b0b": ["Me too. But - Noblestalk. You... you have it?", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "b1419497-8bd8-8b76-23d8-bea4d089059e"], "hc2a5b7cbge892g490dgbaedg0a063b6b1fd1": ["Or - no. Derryth - she's got it. Yes. Right.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "1f22edff-ad73-7acc-b523-35bb39688027"], "h8569c105gf2d4g4292gbad0ge158860bb243": ["Sold it to... to Derryth?", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "81bdc77d-72c5-412c-711e-7f002c4f2452"], "hd4bb7019g2be4g460dg9333gd7a8430cb9e7": ["I forget. Derryth might know. ", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "7b88641e-8d88-7439-fbeb-86f463dee90c"], "h980b98c5gdae5g4b83g9cfagbf513a089c12": ["How did you get trapped to begin with?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "aea71de3-836b-569b-62d2-713b582b83b7"], "h55c1fe64g3491g45bagb137g82a7ef064b5c": ["I... think I... hmm.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "292b8799-19f3-66ec-c555-33d2a513ab8c"], "h134b17d2g3d07g4accg88ddg3ec6e7231576": ["Anywhen. What were we saying?", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "3ec1da04-4bc9-efe2-86ea-f97545f7600f"], "h8b0946dbg4b9eg41ebga194gfef17d842310": ["How did you wind up trapped like that?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "849f06a7-76a5-f635-130b-ce36142c926c"], "h33721153ga10ag4801gbdf7g2a877ab1e367": ["Noblestalk. Yes, Derryth needs Noblestalk. Mushroom. Good stuff.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "ef89c023-0e4f-d406-25fd-e858793b24f3"], "h98bea78ag0c0eg445egb648g1c40cfddc4f0": ["And the ledge... yes, I was on a ledge - crumbled to bits. And I tumbled down.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "6f677bb2-d01c-ef9b-4e91-20891a5829cd"], "hed264d3eg7b34g4323g8ee5gdcbf51ffa7ce": ["You must be keen on mushrooms if you'll willing to brave the Underdark for them.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "85219e5a-071c-a4fe-446f-054b40080314"], "h7fe0d61cg3d00g430agbb62g05365a81d938": ["The shop! The shop needs all we find. Bonecloak's. Baldur's Gate.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "622839be-22b3-8cc6-40a8-41336d2449e7"], "hacadd7ccg4d17g4abega54bgc396b01880fd": ["Anything from - anything sourced here - very high rate of profit.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "a5395012-d9d5-f6ec-c2fd-9514838f6ec5"], "h0ae9fccag7e1ag490agbb39g3bc6c4f07d9d": ["What is Noblestalk, exactly?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "ec47b482-4d60-8242-9b7c-57fa950e9af3"], "h8d8d9969g8c31g47f0g8db5g6e633062fcbe": ["Mushroom. Powerful. Derryth wants it for a brew. ", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "75d6973c-ab42-af1d-5266-632bb1cd52b8"], "h8254950eg6850g4899g9e93g25e339a28817": ["She's very good, my Derryth. Very good at a brew.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "278f9dd2-d7ac-f536-2414-7cc564adf4d3"], "hb17bb911g7ea1g4bccg80fcgc79a3e6e0ebd": ["Apologies, for destroying the Noblestalk.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "2428be90-25b5-85f9-9c12-ae9b1988f10a"], "hbe941a31g8eb9g4ee9g9b2bga9cc5df5099f": ["Wasteful. Very wasteful. What's done is - that is - it's done.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "5bf4547e-52f8-a0a3-56ae-0299adce335d"], "h55783690gb0f8g4acbgb848gde74bea8a755": ["<i>Show him the Noblestalk.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "f256a2b6-bd1c-da85-fd69-4acb21969b5b"], "hc05d7996g5a7fg4a30gb5e1gda052b6a5529": ["Yes! Very much, yes!", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "237d237c-d0a3-f228-bf1d-f4c9bec355e5"], "hcd772137gf4aag4632gb3fdg5063537f80a1": ["Derryth wants it very badly. Very, very badly indeed.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "85f060e8-5abf-7fdf-b218-f5a80e2cd704"], "ha85f62bfgf402g4a4cgbd1fg2c94c02a3cc0": ["Take the Noblestalk and eat it. It'll make you feel better.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "b4d50a7e-c79b-e03f-a6b3-a869c57c52af"], "h988b446agcc2fg4b33g9cbbg759b2202d782": ["<i>Help </i>me? My - yes, my mind isn't what it used to be.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "8cd3fc66-669b-a99c-0daa-183e8fe50341"], "hb8482bf6g24ffg46c9gb7adgacc874a4f0df": ["I could run the shop again. That is - help Derryth.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "8b348886-9693-bc18-24e1-fafb27f4fb1c"], "h78d35537gaebag479agb0ccg167f16996941": ["Ngh... I don't... urgh...", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "cd0b166d-17d0-c4fc-3f6a-a03e8c659116"], "h7a70e072g8547g41acg925bg14a6c2e4ddd3": ["I'll give it to Derryth.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "f1300d81-46bb-d6a3-ebb9-b67ff4791d46"], "h7e98bf0bg70d2g44eeg8306g82c59cb8367f": ["Oh - very glad. She'll be <i>very </i>glad.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "784e3b39-d06a-4239-1923-d78b6343b6a3"], "h9af03c95ga970g4115g8d41g421bb496fb5d": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "d5cdb492-7f68-5ff8-b247-a36dfdc236be"], "hb421b3d3g1728g4720g8581g1232f6916607": ["Did you... take that?", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "febf7570-45ce-ead2-c3e0-501c0095246c"], "h4729ad82g6b66g447cg88d7ge282473d1cff": ["Are you feeling all right? Seems like you get confused easily.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "ab096603-352c-e352-63f5-f3833b16e570"], "h1b73ebcfg6665g479bga2ebg909180610798": ["My, erm - my words get away from me. You'll have to ask Derryth. She knows the ins and outs.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "da05283a-d3e2-91ab-486b-ea476147bfb5"], "he56528b9g326fg4d0cgb59fgfc0bd9b2f52a": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "388cf66e-86c0-eb38-b4e1-d10d96e04922"], "hcf58fbb4ga1ffg4c8fga355g698074a43012": ["You must be a rare breed of fool to go wandering amongst bibberbang.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "1e7d26bc-4756-5695-61ed-ba7950c28a45"], "h96058d72gb315g43a2g9758g249b941e6186": ["Heh. You may be right. And worse - yes, worse by the day.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "59e6f331-fdfe-85d9-6cce-3c39351b438b"], "h21c80c93g9f30g44d7gbe4ag5b66a93a576e": ["Should've waited for Derryth.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "15effd9d-ad12-46d3-e09a-d58c63f42594"], "hef14c983gd40fg4d52ga831g40193c45c214": ["<i>Give him the Noblestalk to eat. It'll help clear his mind.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "684553d8-361e-0c90-4934-c73e0023172f"], "hebe1de4cgbfb3g47d6gbb9eg277bc41d37c9": ["Can't be too careful in these parts. Bibberbang's the least of it.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "2d88e98a-b96a-9cab-89d1-e976cbc6d414"], "ha05f4d61g0a63g4311ga03dgcebea2a53153": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter.html", "39781c19-d6be-ae5c-b12d-1ba6c552830a"]}